I asked, &amp;ldquo;What was so sweet that you’re excited to share?&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>How Do You Want to Live?</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/how-do-you-want-to-live/</link><pubDate>Thu, 27 Apr 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/how-do-you-want-to-live/</guid><description>&lt;p>
